File-Attributes-Recursive

File::Attributes::Recursive works like File::Attributes, but
allows files to inherit attributes from parent directories.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

If make test fails, don't install the module.  File a bug report
instead!

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc File::Attributes::Recursive

You can also look for information at:

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/File-Attributes-Recursive

    CPAN Request Tracker:
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=File-Attributes-Recursive

    AnnoCPAN, annotated CPAN documentation:
        http://annocpan.org/dist/File-Attributes-Recursive

    CPAN Ratings:
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/File-Attributes-Recursive

